# StayScape – Travel Listing Web App
StayScape is a full-stack web application where users can create, edit, and review travel listings.  
Built using Node.js, Express, MongoDB, EJS, and Cloudinary.

## Features
- User Authentication (Login / Signup)
- Create, Edit, Delete Listings
- Upload Images using Cloudinary
- Add and Delete Reviews
- Authorization (Owner only edit/delete)
- Flash Messages
- Map integration
- Responsive UI with Bootstrap

## Tech Stack
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- Mongoose
- EJS
- Bootstrap
- Cloudinary
- Multer
- Passport.js
- Express Session


## Installation
1. Clone the repository:-git clone https://github.com/yourusername/stayscape.git
2. Go to project folder :-cd stayscape
3. Install dependencies:-npm install
4. Create .env file

Add the following:

CLOUD_NAME=your_cloud_name
CLOUD_API_KEY=your_key
CLOUD_API_SECRET=your_secret

5. Run the server
nodemon app.js

6. Open in browser
http://localhost:8080


## Folder Structure

models/
routes/
controllers/
views/
public/
cloudConfig.js
app.js

